{"tid":952970,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)月光光心慌慌 銀魂2 今天不殺狗","createTime":"2018-12-23T14:36:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T19:57:46.000Z","uid":29160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7fca77ca78e3b81f0ca05848d021e0d9b839e4","tid":952970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3UjhgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2d1d8cf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3UjhgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bb22c16d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3UjhgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d619daf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b0/Halloween_2018_poster.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb0%2FHalloween_2018_poster.png&h=383865ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/5e/Gintama_2_Okite_wa_Yaburu_tame_ni_koso_Aru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F5e%2FGintama_2_Okite_wa_Yaburu_tame_ni_koso_Aru.jpg&h=f96090f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/dd/Replicas_2018_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fdd%2FReplicas_2018_Poster.jpg&h=fdd5107f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.洛莉&middot;史特羅德在從麥克&middot;邁爾斯的手中逃出後，麥克一直以來被關在監獄中；但未料，相隔四十年後，麥克從獄中逃脫並再度戴上面具，打算展開久違的殺戮<br />\n<br />\n2.由原作動畫｢真選組暗殺篇｣為主線劇情，並另外搭配短篇搞笑日常組成。 真選組副長土方十四郎在護衛將軍的過程中，遭遇浪士偷襲，脖子被植入晶片，以至於行為御宅化，對於二次元事物無法抗拒，洽逢真選組參謀&mdash;伊東鴨太郎歸隊，野心勃勃的伊東策劃排擠土方，並與鬼兵隊聯手，企圖在列車上暗殺組長近藤勳。 土方在意識清醒時委託萬事屋保護真選組，阿銀一行人也因此意外捲入事件，並在過程中意外發現鬼兵隊河上萬齋等人的真正陰謀<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述當神經科科學家威爾&middot;佛斯特的家人在車禍中不幸遇難時，他即將成功地將人類意識轉移到電腦之中。為了讓他們復活，威爾招募同伴科學家艾德幫助他秘密製作出其複製體。但當他發現他們只能讓四個家庭成員中的三人復活時，威爾陷入了苦澀的抉擇和考驗，同時這使他也得面臨國家單位的追查<br />\n<br />\n10 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3UjhgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c8ccc1f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=dzXL1%2FGw5IWxb47Be3UjhgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7ef5bb45\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390595edf4b069abc1ead463f8bd107370abbb79","tid":952970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite